To make cells count: i32, giving owned buffer of i32.
Let cells be owned buffer of count i32 filled with 2.
Give cells.

To nested caller flag: i1, giving i32.
Let result be 0.
When flag: Let cells be make cells 4; result becomes length of cells.
Otherwise: result becomes 1.
Give result.

To main, giving i32.
Give nested caller true.
